milestones.description: Asa Tribe and Lawrenson's 232-run partnership is JER's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Asa Tribe and Lawrenson
Asa Tribe and Lawrenson's 232-run partnership is JER's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 81 between Lawrenson and Greenwood
Lawrenson has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for JER breaking Greenwood's record
Lawrenson has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (56) in an innings in ODIs for JER, going past Greenwood's 32
Asa Tribe's 115 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for JER), surpassing Jonty Jenner's 76
Sumerauer has conceded the most runs in an innings (69) in ODIs for JER, going past Anthony Hawkins-Kay's record of 58
Carlyon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for JER, going past Jake Dunford
